50|$|In December 2002, Natural Resources Canada (NRCan) {{selected}} Hydrogenics {{to develop}} a next-generation hybrid fuel cells bus; Hydrogenics integrated its <b>vehicle-to-grid</b> technology into a 12.5 meter New Flyer Inverno 40i transit bus. Hydrogenics' FC Hybrid Tecnobus midibus was exhibited in Europe in 2005.|$|E
