50|$|Developing electric-vehicles {{will assist}} energy {{conservation}} {{and security in}} China since energy efficiency is 46% {{higher than that of}} internal combustion engines (ICEs). Electric-vehicles also have the potential to reduce carbon dioxide emissions by 13-68%: directly, through advanced V2G (<b>vehicle-to-grid)</b> technology and indirectly, through peak shaving.|$|E
